  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You&rsquo;re not a native Osirian, but the opportunity to explore the tombs of Ancient Osirion&mdash;and &ldquo;liberate&rdquo; the treasures they hold&mdash;is too good to pass up. Whether or not you&rsquo;re interested in the history of this land, you&rsquo;re def initely interested in the wealth that&rsquo;s lain hidden in dusty crypts for millennia&mdash; such as the tombs in the newly opened necropolis of Wati.</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\">You gain a +2 trait bonus on Appraise checks, and that skill is always a class skill for you. In addition, your contacts in the antiquities markets allow you to sell relics of Ancient Osirion for 60% of their listed price, rather than the normal 50% value. What is considered a relic of Ancient Osirion is left to the GM&rsquo;s discretion.</span></p>",
